《聖經》前情提要
Previously on The Bible.

3
00:00:14,097 --> 00:00:16,316
起初
In the beginning,

4
00:00:16,391 --> 00:00:20,612
上帝創造天地
God created the heavens and the earth.

5
00:00:22,189 --> 00:00:27,160
亞當和夏娃違背了上帝的旨意偷食了禁果
Adam and Eve disobeyed God and ate the forbidden fruit.

6
00:00:27,236 --> 00:00:31,286
從那之後  因為該隱殺了亞伯
Since then, since Cain killed Abel,

7
00:00:31,365 --> 00:00:34,869
上帝目睹了人類內心深處太多的惡念
God has seen too much evil in human hearts.

8
00:00:34,952 --> 00:00:38,957
上帝警告我  要我造一艘船
God warned me. He told me to build a boat.

9
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:50,301
亞伯拉罕
Abraham.

10
00:00:50,968 --> 00:00:53,096
上帝對我說話了
God has spoken to me.

11
00:00:53,178 --> 00:00:56,352
他將指引我們去新的家園
He will lead us to a new home.

12
00:00:56,431 --> 00:00:59,685
他保證我的後裔會多如繁星
He has promised descendants as numerous as the stars.

13
00:00:59,810 --> 00:01:02,063
你會有孩子的   我不會有
You will have a child. I can't.

14
00:01:02,145 --> 00:01:03,988
我的年紀太大了
It's too late for me.

15
00:01:04,064 --> 00:01:08,194
亞伯拉罕  土地不夠   我們人太多了
Abraham, there just isn't enough land. There are too many of us.

16
00:01:08,277 --> 00:01:09,529
是時候分道揚鑣了
It's time we go our separate ways.

17
00:01:09,611 --> 00:01:12,285
發生了什麼事   他們人太多了
- What happened? - There were so many of them.

18
00:01:12,364 --> 00:01:16,915
羅得呢   還活著   但被抓走了
- And Lot? - Alive. But taken prisoner.

19
00:01:16,994 --> 00:01:22,342
如果我連自己的家人都領導不了  又如何去領導一個民族呢
How can I lead a people when I can't even lead my own family?

20
00:01:22,416 --> 00:01:25,295
相信上帝
Trust in God!

21
00:01:28,922 --> 00:01:31,926
亞伯拉罕   我們還是要去所多瑪
Abraham, we're carrying on to Sodom.

22
00:01:32,009 --> 00:01:35,138
你們要毀滅它嗎   整座城市
You're going to destroy it. The whole city?

23
00:01:40,976 --> 00:01:46,028
殲滅惡人的同時也要消滅那些好人嗎
Will you destroy the good men along with the evil ones?

24
00:01:55,490 --> 00:01:58,118
亞伯拉罕  你的妻子在哪兒
Abraham, where is your wife?

25
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:01,250
雖然她老了  撒拉會生下一個男孩
Though she is barren, Sarah will have a son.

26
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:03,458
要給他起名叫做以撒
You will name him Isaac.

27
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:05,463
上帝要你去獻祭
God wants a sacrifice.

28
00:02:05,542 --> 00:02:08,716
你還不相信我的忠誠嗎
Have I not shown you enough faith?

29
00:02:08,795 --> 00:02:10,047
亞伯拉罕
Abraham!

30
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:23,719
《聖經》
第02集-出埃及記

31
00:02:28,023 --> 00:02:31,277
經過近400年的亞伯拉罕
Nearly 400 years after Abraham,

32
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:35,740
飢荒迫使以色列人遠離應許之地  來到埃及
famine has forced the Israelites from the promised land to Egypt.

33
00:02:37,741 --> 00:02:40,745
在那裡  他們成為了法老的奴隸
Here they've been enslaved by Pharaoh.

34
00:02:45,539 --> 00:02:49,386
亞伯拉罕和上帝成了遙遠的記憶
Abraham and God have become a distant memory.

35
00:02:50,671 --> 00:02:54,642
他的子民都淪為役畜
All his people reduced to beasts of burden,

36
00:02:57,344 --> 00:02:59,142
只有一人幸免於難
except one.

37
00:03:02,850 --> 00:03:05,021
摩西
Moses.

38
00:03:09,106 --> 00:03:11,108
你不能再去爭強斗勇了   我無法拒絕
- You're not going to fight again. - I can't refuse.

39
00:03:11,191 --> 00:03:13,193
母親  他是法老的兒子
He's Pharaohs son, Mother.

40
00:03:23,286 --> 00:03:25,254
他們之間的較量必須停止
The fighting between them has to stop.

41
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:29,961
摩西並不想去   是你兒子逼他的  屢敗屢戰
Moses doesn't want to fight. It's your son who forces him into it and keeps losing.

42
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,598
也許你是我姐姐的心頭寶
You may be my sister's favourite,

43
00:03:42,681 --> 00:03:44,183
但我才是未來的法老
but I will be Pharaoh.

44
00:03:44,266 --> 00:03:47,110
我會是埃及的神
I will be god!

45
00:03:50,814 --> 00:03:54,489
別打了   還手  我命令你
- Please. - Fight me! I order you!

46
00:04:04,286 --> 00:04:06,288
摩西
Moses.

47
00:04:06,371 --> 00:04:07,918
夠了
Enough!

48
00:04:07,998 --> 00:04:09,375
啊
Ahh!

49
00:04:15,297 --> 00:04:18,301
他得明白自己的身份   是你先開始的
- He needs to learn his place. - You were the one that started...

50
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:19,885
我是未來的法老王
I will be Pharaoh!

51
00:04:19,968 --> 00:04:23,973
那麼你的行為處事最好有個法老王的樣子
Then you better start behaving like one.

52
00:04:24,055 --> 00:04:26,558
都是你的錯  你就不該讓姐姐撫養他
This is your fault. You should never have let her keep him.

53
00:04:26,641 --> 00:04:27,984
閉嘴
Silence.

54
00:04:28,059 --> 00:04:29,936
你根本不是我族人
You're not one of us.

55
00:04:30,061 --> 00:04:32,905
我叫你閉嘴   他在說什麼
Silence, I said! What's he talking about?

56
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:41,782
你最好現在就告訴他
You'd better tell him now.

57
00:04:50,165 --> 00:04:51,712
你
You!

58
00:04:53,043 --> 00:04:55,216
跟我過來
Come with me!

59
00:05:00,050 --> 00:05:02,553
母親  告訴我什麼
Mother, tell me what?

60
00:05:03,970 --> 00:05:05,722
什麼啊
What?

61
00:05:08,266 --> 00:05:12,021
摩西   我把你當兒子一樣疼愛
Moses, I love you like a son.

62
00:05:15,273 --> 00:05:17,742
但是你並非我親生
But you're not my blood.

63
00:05:19,945 --> 00:05:22,164
你是奴隸之子
You were born a slave.

64
00:05:26,076 --> 00:05:29,205
把他們都抓來
Take them all!

65
00:05:33,625 --> 00:05:36,595
我父親殺了很多孩子
Father killed so many children.

66
00:05:39,506 --> 00:05:41,099
他擔心會有叛亂
He feared a rebellion.

67
00:05:42,968 --> 00:05:44,891
你的族人數量太多了
Your people were too many.

68
00:05:47,347 --> 00:05:50,897
我的   人民
My... - People?

69
00:05:50,976 --> 00:05:52,944
我救了你
I saved you.

70
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:10,500
你的人民就在外面  摩西
Your people are out there, Moses.

71
00:06:10,579 --> 00:06:12,627
我們的奴隸
Our slaves.

72
00:06:14,206 --> 00:06:16,460
那些以色列人
The Israelites.

73
00:06:26,928 --> 00:06:30,023
你有個哥哥  叫亞倫
You had a brother- Aaron.

74
00:06:31,141 --> 00:06:34,611
還有一個姐姐   叫米利暗
And a sister- Miriam.

75
00:06:36,438 --> 00:06:38,782
但他們跟我們不一樣
But they are not like us.

76
00:06:38,899 --> 00:06:41,823
快點  你  快點
Come on! You! Move along!

77
00:06:42,903 --> 00:06:44,746
快點  快起來  婊子
Come on! You'll get more!

78
00:06:44,821 --> 00:06:47,415
他們崇拜亞伯拉罕的神
They worship the God of Abraham.

79
00:06:47,490 --> 00:06:49,709
而祂拋棄了他們
And he has deserted them.

80
00:07:00,921 --> 00:07:03,424
起來   停
Get up! Stop.

81
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:05,474
以色列賤民
Israelite scum!

82
00:07:06,927 --> 00:07:09,476
不要  求求你  我求你了
No, please! Please, I beg of you!

83
00:07:10,889 --> 00:07:13,517
狗奴才
Dog!

84
00:07:32,535 --> 00:07:34,629
快跑  快跑
Run. Run.

85
00:07:34,704 --> 00:07:36,331
我會把屍體藏起來
I will hide the body.

86
00:08:03,149 --> 00:08:06,153
主人  這是摩西的護身符
My lord, the amulet of Moses.

87
00:08:07,028 --> 00:08:09,531
要不要追捕他   不
Shall we hunt him down? No.

88
00:08:10,573 --> 00:08:13,417
讓他走   他已經不會造成威脅了
Let him go. He's no threat now.

89
00:08:15,078 --> 00:08:18,503
歡迎進入你的新生活  摩西
Welcome to your new life, Moses!

90
00:08:18,581 --> 00:08:20,754
你現在什麼都不是了
You are nothing now!

91
00:08:23,586 --> 00:08:25,259
什麼都不是
Nothing.

92
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:04,711
你的子民都在外面呢  摩西
Your people are out there, Moses.

93
00:09:04,794 --> 00:09:08,139
你非我族人
You're not one of us.

94
00:09:09,507 --> 00:09:12,636
他們崇拜亞伯拉罕的神
They worship the God of Abraham.

95
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:15,018
你不應該讓她收留他
You should never have let' her keep him.

96
00:09:15,096 --> 00:09:17,690
祂拋棄了他們
And he has deserted them.

97
00:09:17,766 --> 00:09:19,313
我會成為法老
I will be Pharaoh!

98
00:09:38,787 --> 00:09:40,710
摩西
Moses.

99
00:09:58,681 --> 00:10:00,184
摩西
Moses.

100
00:10:18,284 --> 00:10:19,786
我在這
I am here.

101
00:10:19,869 --> 00:10:25,046
我是亞伯拉罕  以撒和雅各的神
I am the God of Abraham, of Isaac and Jacob.

102
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:28,048
你是真實存在的嗎   是的
You are real? I am.

103
00:10:29,129 --> 00:10:31,973
我看到我的子民所受的痛苦
I have seen the misery of my people.

104
00:10:32,048 --> 00:10:35,928
我派你到法老那裡去   帶他們離開埃及
I am sending you to Pharaoh to bring them out of Egypt.

105
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:39,139
但是我要怎麼做才能讓他們自由
But how can I set them free?

106
00:10:39,222 --> 00:10:41,520
我現在不是一個王子
I'm not a prince now.

107
00:10:41,599 --> 00:10:43,852
我什麼都不是
I'm nothing.

108
00:10:43,935 --> 00:10:46,939
我會與你同在
I will be with you.

109
00:11:03,079 --> 00:11:04,956
有了你的力量
With your power,

110
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:08,509
我會讓我的人民獲得自由
I will set my people free.

111
00:11:19,512 --> 00:11:23,233
在埃及  新王已經登基
In Egypt, there is a new man on the throne.

112
00:11:26,144 --> 00:11:30,570
摩西的老對手已經成了法老王
Moses' old rival is now Pharaoh.

113
00:11:44,454 --> 00:11:46,001
謝謝你  父親
Thank you, Father.

114
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:50,426
終有一天  你會擁有一支軍隊   真正的軍隊
One day you will have an army of them. Real ones.

115
00:12:14,067 --> 00:12:15,944
快幹活   快幹活
- Come on! - Come on!

116
00:12:27,288 --> 00:12:29,086
一切如昨
Nothing has changed.

117
00:12:29,206 --> 00:12:32,177
仍舊水深火熱
So much suffering. Please!

118
00:12:38,341 --> 00:12:41,265
你   你
Hey, Wu! Hey, you!

119
00:12:42,804 --> 00:12:44,226
回去幹活
Back to work!

120
00:12:44,305 --> 00:12:47,730
繼續  幹活
Go on! Move it!

121
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:51,904
等等  請等等
Wait. Wait. Please.

122
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:53,903
我來跟他說  大人
I'll take care of him, master.

123
00:12:57,193 --> 00:13:00,322
你在幹什麼  想讓我們都挨打嗎
What are you doing? Trying to get us all a beating?

124
00:13:02,907 --> 00:13:04,454
你是誰
Who are you?

125
00:13:04,575 --> 00:13:07,920
你在這幹什麼   我是摩西
What are you doing here? My name is Moses.

126
00:13:12,292 --> 00:13:13,919
摩西
Moses.

127
00:13:14,002 --> 00:13:16,175
你就是摩西
You are Moses?

128
00:13:18,131 --> 00:13:19,929
我要見你們的長老
I need to see your elders.

129
00:13:23,553 --> 00:13:25,351
跟我來
Come with me.

130
00:13:40,945 --> 00:13:43,414
這人說他是摩西
This man says he's Moses!

131
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:48,504
那個逃跑的王子
The Runaway Prince.

132
00:13:49,954 --> 00:13:51,797
你因犯謀殺罪被通緝
You're wanted for murder.

133
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:57,630
如果你真是他  為什麼回來
If you're who you say you are, why would you return?

134
00:14:01,132 --> 00:14:04,261
上帝派我回來的
God has sent me.

135
00:14:06,262 --> 00:14:08,685
我到這兒來
I am here

136
00:14:08,765 --> 00:14:10,984
給你們自由
to set you free.

137
00:14:12,352 --> 00:14:14,229
上帝派你來的
God has sent you?

138
00:14:14,312 --> 00:14:16,030
沒錯
Yes. God...

139
00:14:16,105 --> 00:14:19,484
上帝派我來  向你們傳話
sent me to speak to you.

140
00:14:21,819 --> 00:14:23,787
你們還記得上帝嗎
Have you forgotten God?

141
00:14:25,448 --> 00:14:27,621
即使你們忘記了他
Even if you have...

142
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:31,629
他卻未曾忘記你們
He has not forgotten you.

143
00:14:31,704 --> 00:14:33,548
恐怕你忘記了
In case you had forgotten,

144
00:14:33,623 --> 00:14:37,548
法老才是我們唯一讓我們害怕的神
Pharaoh is the only god we have to fear.

145
00:14:37,627 --> 00:14:40,096
你認為他會輕易放我們走嗎
And you think he's just going to let us go?

146
00:14:40,171 --> 00:14:42,014
是誰創造了大地
Who created the earth,

147
00:14:43,674 --> 00:14:45,221
海洋
sea,

148
00:14:45,301 --> 00:14:47,679
天空
the sky?

149
00:14:47,762 --> 00:14:49,515
是誰創造了你們
Who created you?

150
00:14:51,557 --> 00:14:53,150
法老王
Pharaoh?

151
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:56,112
還是上帝
Or God?

152
00:14:56,187 --> 00:14:59,407
你瘋了  不
You're demented. No.

153
00:15:01,275 --> 00:15:02,902
他沒有
He isn't.

154
00:15:07,115 --> 00:15:08,788
他是我的弟弟
He's my brother

155
00:15:10,201 --> 00:15:11,373
亞倫
Aaron.

156
00:15:13,329 --> 00:15:14,876
摩西
Moses!

157
00:15:19,419 --> 00:15:21,638
上帝向我托夢
God sent me a dream...

158
00:15:21,712 --> 00:15:24,591
說你會回來
to say you would return.

159
00:15:24,674 --> 00:15:27,223
這是米利暗  你的姐姐
This is Miriam, your sister.

160
00:15:29,512 --> 00:15:30,684
弟弟
Brother.

161
00:15:34,809 --> 00:15:36,607
這是我的孩子
My children.

162
00:15:43,317 --> 00:15:45,661
我的家人
My family.

163
00:15:45,736 --> 00:15:48,239
我的子民
My people

164
00:15:48,322 --> 00:15:50,495
我們的子民
Our people.

165
00:15:52,201 --> 00:15:55,546
-上帝的子民  -上帝的子民
- God's people! - God's people!

166
00:15:58,374 --> 00:16:01,002
老法老王或許喜歡你
Old Pharaoh may have been fond of you,

167
00:16:01,085 --> 00:16:04,715
但你現在要對付的是他的兒子
But it's his son you'll have to deal with now.

168
00:16:05,798 --> 00:16:08,551
法老為什麼要見你
Why would Pharaoh even see you?

169
00:16:08,634 --> 00:16:10,557
Oh.

170
00:16:13,723 --> 00:16:16,067
他會想見我的
He'll want to see me.

171
00:17:16,285 --> 00:17:18,208
你有兒子
You have a son.

172
00:17:18,287 --> 00:17:19,504
有繼承人了  
An heir.

173
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:22,629
我們的王朝將千秋萬代
Our dynasty will last forever.

174
00:17:32,134 --> 00:17:33,636
你到這兒來做什麼  摩西
Why are you here, Moses?

175
00:17:33,719 --> 00:17:37,144
來請求寬恕嗎
Have you come to ask for forgiveness?

176
00:17:37,223 --> 00:17:38,520
不  
No.

177
00:17:38,599 --> 00:17:42,775
上帝出於某種目的救了我
God saved me for a purpose.

178
00:17:43,854 --> 00:17:44,855
是嗎
Yes?

179
00:17:47,316 --> 00:17:52,698
我是來要求你還他的子民自由的
I come to demand that you release his people from slavery.

180
00:17:55,491 --> 00:17:57,164
要求
Demand?

181
00:17:58,202 --> 00:18:00,500
讓我的子民離開
Let my people go.

182
00:18:02,873 --> 00:18:05,296
你一直是名鬥士  摩西
You always were a fighter, Moses.

183
00:18:05,376 --> 00:18:08,596
但你戰敗時從不自知
But you never knew when you were beaten.

184
00:18:08,671 --> 00:18:10,765
倘若藐視上帝
If you defy God,

185
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:12,968
你會受到懲罰
you will be punished.

186
00:18:14,176 --> 00:18:17,646
這麼多年後  你回來就為了威脅我嗎
