00:42:20,163 --> 00:42:23,007
上帝將刻在石頭上的法典
God gives laws to Moses...

384
00:42:23,082 --> 00:42:25,585
賜予了摩西
written in stone.

385
00:42:28,463 --> 00:42:30,886
這就是《十誡》
The Ten Commandments.

386
00:42:39,891 --> 00:42:41,437
約書亞
Joshua.

387
00:42:49,650 --> 00:42:51,027
上帝
God has...

388
00:42:52,779 --> 00:42:56,659
重申了他對亞伯拉罕許下的承諾
Renewed the promise he made to Abraham.

389
00:42:58,076 --> 00:43:02,297
我們有了可以在應許之地實行的新法典 
We have new laws preparing us for the promised land.

390
00:43:03,456 --> 00:43:08,257
如果我們忠於上帝  他一定會遵守諾言
If we are true to God, he will keep his promise.

391
00:43:08,336 --> 00:43:10,213
亞伯拉罕的夢想
Abraham's dream.

392
00:43:11,464 --> 00:43:13,887
我們的未來
Our future.

393
00:43:13,966 --> 00:43:16,810
你是我們人民的未來  約書亞
You are our people's future, Joshua.

394
00:43:16,886 --> 00:43:21,767
你必須延續上帝對亞伯拉罕所立
You must take the land promised to Abraham...

395
00:43:21,849 --> 00:43:24,227
和他如繁星般多的後裔
and all of his descendants,

396
00:43:25,228 --> 00:43:28,152
所立的約
as numerous as the stars.

397
00:43:40,952 --> 00:43:43,080
下集《聖經》預告
Next time on The Bible.

398
00:43:44,330 --> 00:43:47,049
耶和華帶我們離開了埃及
The Lord brought us out from Egypt.

399
00:43:47,125 --> 00:43:49,469
他承諾將賜予我們這塊土地
He promised us this land.

400
00:43:49,544 --> 00:43:52,673
很快  它就會是我們的了
Soon, it will be ours.

401
00:43:52,755 --> 00:43:54,257
我們必須攻下耶利哥
We must take Jericho.

402
00:43:54,340 --> 00:43:55,762
找一條能讓我進去的路
Just find me a way in.

403
00:43:57,510 --> 00:43:59,558
約書亞
Joshua!

404
00:43:59,637 --> 00:44:02,311
他們知道上帝與我們同在  都陷入恐慌  不戰自潰
The people melt in fear because they know he is with us.

405
00:44:02,390 --> 00:44:04,233
上帝與我們同在
God is with us.

406
00:44:05,518 --> 00:44:08,863
耶和華為摩西將海水分開
The Lord parted the waters for Moses.

407
00:44:08,937 --> 00:44:12,067
而為你  他將讓岩石碎裂
For you, he will split rock.

408
00:44:18,197 --> 00:44:19,948
耶利哥是我們的
Jericho is ours!

409
00:44:22,994 --> 00:44:25,713
如果我們聽從上帝的指引
If we obey the Lord,

410
00:44:25,788 --> 00:44:28,837
一切皆有可能
anything is possible!

411
00:44:28,916 --> 00:44:30,293
以色列
Israel!

412
00:44:30,376 --> 00:44:33,550
以色列  以色列
Israel! Israel!

413
00:44:35,173 --> 00:44:36,766
上帝會允你一個兒子
God will give you a son.

414
00:44:38,801 --> 00:44:40,929
你的力量源自上帝
Your strength comes from God.

415
00:44:41,012 --> 00:44:43,185
參孫
Samson,

416
00:44:43,265 --> 00:44:47,861
"你背負著趕走非利士人的使命"
your duty is to drive the Philistines away.

417
00:44:47,935 --> 00:44:50,063
您想讓我怎麼辦
What would you have me do?

418
00:44:50,146 --> 00:44:53,696
拋棄我愛的女人  就因為她是非利士人嗎
Reject the woman I fell in love with just because she's a Philistine?

419
00:44:53,774 --> 00:44:57,574
我們得給以色列人點顏色瞧瞧  我們的女人不是他們可以染指的
We need to send these Israelites a message. They cannot take our women.

420
00:45:00,031 --> 00:45:01,408
為吾妻
For my wife.

421
00:45:13,461 --> 00:45:14,963
你叫什麼名字
What is your name?

422
00:45:15,046 --> 00:45:17,720
我叫大利拉
My name is Delilah.

423
00:45:17,798 --> 00:45:20,051
你為何如此強壯
Why are you so strong?

424
00:45:21,302 --> 00:45:23,020
上帝與我同在  大利拉
God is with me, Delilah.

425
00:45:24,472 --> 00:45:26,600
他賜我神力
He makes me strong.

426
00:45:27,183 --> 00:45:29,402
倘若我剪了頭髮
If I cut my hair,

427
00:45:29,477 --> 00:45:31,605
上帝會收回我的神力
my God will take away all my strength.

428
00:45:33,231 --> 00:45:35,199
你做了什麼
What have you done!

429
00:45:35,274 --> 00:45:37,527
每個人都有自己的價碼
Everyone has their price.

430
00:45:39,862 --> 00:45:42,956
你的上帝拋棄了你
Your God has deserted you...

431
00:45:43,032 --> 00:45:45,831
收回了你的神力
and taken your strength with him.

432
00:45:47,078 --> 00:45:51,504
不  他要我徹底毀了你們
No. He wants me to destroy you all!

